WIP Quick quickstart
****************

/--div .[perex]
Get to know *Nette Framework*.
In this series we will create a very simple *blog* - a website, where you can add new blog posts, users can read and comment on them.
\--

You can start very quickly. After first two chapters you will have your own blog working and you'll be ready to publish awesome posts. Though the features are pretty much limited after there two chapters. To make it nicer for your users, you may read also the following chapters and keep improving your app.

To save the data, we will use *mysql* database, because it is the most common choice among web developers. But if you don’t like it, feel free to use database of your choice.


